data.description: WOW! Nestled on 1.5 acres in the city, this gem is truly one of a kind. Entering this home you will find an inviting foyer, light and bright library, heated 3 season room, oak flooring throughout, formal living room with wood burning fireplace, cozy heated sunroom, formal dining room with built-ins, 1/2 bath and a renovated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, lots of cabinet space and an eat-in area. The second floor offers a large master bedroom with an updated full bath, 2 large bedrooms, full guest bath and a bonus room that can be used as a 4th bedroom or a home office. The interior also features a partially finished basement with a built-in pool table and a large walk up attic that can be used for storage or can easily be finished. The sellers have spared no expense with their improvments including-newer roof, new HVAC system, all baths renovated. The list goes on and on. Lets not forget about the outside! Features include- attached 2 car garage, fully fenced in-ground pool and a pool house with a 1/2 bath. Conveniently located to public and private schools, hospital and doctors offices and all of your favorite shops. From the moment you walk in,you'll feel right at home!
